<L>__{interior power and enterprise committee day}
<A>__{a hundred or so members of the public trade groups, hill staffers, lawyers, tourists settle into their seats. van dyke escorts hattie rifkin and a busload of silver foxes. loretta comes in with ellen and mickey juba. grandma comes in, on reinhardt's arm. she is dressed up as a biddy, down to a hat with fruit on it. committee members head for their seats at the dais. olaf andersen is at the witness table, along with a couple of other businessmen. in a seat behind andersen, tommy o'connor. the press. a good turnout, with several camera crews.}
<D>__{washington reporter #1 you know what this is? washington reporter #2}
