<B>__{on ellen and mickey juba}
<C>__{tommy }
<D>__{... the plain people who just want peace of mind who just want to know they're raising their kids in safe neighborhoods and sending them to safe schools.}
<A>__{on the dais dodge wants to wrap this up.}
<C>__{tommy}
