<D>__{dodge double crossed us.}
<C>__{andersen}
<D>__{you're fired.}
<B>__{on tommy}
<C>__{tommy}
<D>__{one million dollars, if we would stop the epa from investigating the connection between power lines and cancer clusters.}
<A>__{shocked murmurs sweep the room. reinhardt is aghast. homer and armando are delighted.}
<C>__{tommy}
<D>__{isn't that right, mr. andersen?}
<A>__{tommy flicks his eyebrows at andersen, provocatively, imitating dodge.}
<C>__{andersen}
<D>__{that's a vicious lie.}
